<paragraph id="8B8036D20530B168FD4AD62EFC97FB3E" blockId="16.[675,1211,501,1256]" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">
L’échantillon 
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FCD7D62EFC06FDF9" box="[824,1005,533,559]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Malcomber 2655</emphasis>
, 
<typeStatus id="548488700530B168FC13D62EFBC1FDF9" box="[1020,1066,533,559]" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">type</typeStatus>
de 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D510530B168FBBBD62EFCF9FD99" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Pandanus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="barbellatus">
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FBBBD62EFCF9FD99" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Pandanus barbellatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<typeStatus id="548488700530B168FCF1D60EFCA7FD99" box="[798,844,565,591]" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">type</typeStatus>
de la subsection 
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FC18D60EFBB1FD99" box="[1015,1114,565,591]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Barbellati</emphasis>
Huynh), a été placé dans la section 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D510530B168FC5CD66EFB5DFDB9" authority="(Huynh 1998)" baseAuthorityName="Huynh" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[947,1206,597,623]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Foullioya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FC5CD66EFBFAFDB9" box="[947,1041,597,623]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Foullioya</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFAE4B230530B168FBF1D66EFB45FDB9" author="HUYNH K. - L." box="[1054,1198,597,623]" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" pagination="53 - 60" refId="ref12575" refString="HUYNH K. - L. 1998. - The genus Pandanus (Pandanaceae) in Madagascar (part 2). Bulletin de la Societe neuchateloise des Sciences naturelles 121: 53 - 60." type="journal article" year="1998">Huynh 1998</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Sa feuille très coriace, large de 
<quantity id="4CC79B370530B168FC1DD64FFBAAFD58" box="[1010,1089,628,654]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" unit="cm" value="3.5">3,5 cm</quantity>
, longue de 
<quantity id="4CC79B370530B168FD4AD6AFFCC0FD78" box="[677,811,660,686]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.375" metricValueMax="1.4" metricValueMin="1.35" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" unit="cm" value="137.5" valueMax="140.0" valueMin="135.0">135-140 cm</quantity>
et la présence d’une grande auricule sont des caractères inconnus dans cette section. La dimension et la forme des syncarpes (oblong-ovoïdes de 
<quantity id="4CC79B370530B168FD00D6C8FCCDFCDB" box="[751,806,755,781]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" unit="cm" value="8.0">8 cm</quantity>
de longueur et 
<quantity id="4CC79B370530B168FC3ED6C8FBF6FCDB" box="[977,1053,755,781]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" unit="cm" value="5.5">5,5 cm</quantity>
de largeur), le nombre de drupes par syncarpe (environ 600 drupes) sont autant d’autres caractères qui n’ont rien en commun avec la section révisée ici. Cette espèce possède toutes les caractéristiques de la section 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D510530B168FB6DD749FD17FC7A" authorityName="Arnback-Christie-Linde" authorityYear="1924" class="Ascidiacea" family="Pyuridae" genus="Heterostigma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stolidobranchia" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FB6DD749FD17FC7A" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Heterostigma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comme l’auteur l’avait déjà pressenti lors de sa description (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAE4B230530B168FC8DD78AFBF6FC1D" author="HUYNH K. - L." box="[866,1053,945,971]" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" pagination="53 - 60" refId="ref12575" refString="HUYNH K. - L. 1998. - The genus Pandanus (Pandanaceae) in Madagascar (part 2). Bulletin de la Societe neuchateloise des Sciences naturelles 121: 53 - 60." type="journal article" year="1998">Huynh 1998: 60</bibRefCitation>
). L’immaturité de son syncarpe entraîne la forme particulière du stigmate (deux lobes très recourbés) (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAE4B230530B168FBC9D7CBFD2AFBFC" author="HUYNH K. - L." pageId="16" pageNumber="55" pagination="53 - 60" refId="ref12575" refString="HUYNH K. - L. 1998. - The genus Pandanus (Pandanaceae) in Madagascar (part 2). Bulletin de la Societe neuchateloise des Sciences naturelles 121: 53 - 60." type="journal article" year="1998">Huynh 1998: 59</bibRefCitation>
, fig. 14) et ceci a amené l’auteur à placer ce taxon dans une nouvelle subsection 
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FC0CD00BFBA1FB9C" box="[995,1098,1072,1098]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Barbellati</emphasis>
au sein de la section 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D510530B168FCE1D06BFC86FBBC" baseAuthorityName="Huynh" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[782,877,1104,1130]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Foullioya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FCE1D06BFC86FBBC" box="[782,877,1104,1130]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Foullioya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. La ressemblance des stigmates des sections 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D510530B168FCDFD054FC7AFB5F" baseAuthorityName="Huynh" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[816,913,1135,1161]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Foullioya" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FCDFD054FC7AFB5F" box="[816,913,1135,1161]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Foullioya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="4C3F4D510530B168FC58D054FBAAFB5F" authorityName="Arnback-Christie-Linde" authorityYear="1924" box="[951,1089,1135,1161]" class="Ascidiacea" family="Pyuridae" genus="Heterostigma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stolidobranchia" pageId="16" pageNumber="55" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FC58D054FBAAFB5F" box="[951,1089,1135,1161]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">Heterostigma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
durant les premiers stades du développement avait déjà été signalée par Pichi-Sermolli (
<emphasis id="B94BEAC00530B168FC34D094FC1AFB1F" box="[987,1009,1199,1225]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="55">in</emphasis>
Martelli &amp; Pichi- Sermolli 1951: 97).
</paragraph>
